videos.headline: Mountaineers RB pounces to end zone for TD
videos.description: Appalachian State running back Jalin Moore takes the handoff and powers his way to the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Thomas finesses into end zone for 2nd rush TD
videos.description: Zac Thomas shows off his mobility and dives into the end zone for a Mountaineers touchdown, his second on the ground.

videos.headline: Thomas finds wide-open WR for 27-yard TD
videos.description: App State QB Zac Thomas continues his impressive first half with his fourth total touchdown, hitting Marcus Williams Jr. for a 27-yard score.
